{"tid":606037,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【美帝恩賜】NBA將會向前樂視體育NBA付費會員免費提供NBA League Pass","createTime":"2018-03-26T07:42:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-26T11:08:34.000Z","uid":60281,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"99bf4506bc4a34dfd23bb9ea6563bd19713c07e7","tid":606037,"uid":60281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T07:42:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n樂視體育香港在本月中「熄燈」，nowTV已接手直播英超，但NBA直播權仍未有電視台接手，令一班NBA球迷大為不滿。NBA周一發表聲明，指前樂視體育NBA付費會員在香港地區可通過NBA League Pass觀看賽事，惟所有賽事及內容均為英文旁述。<br />\n<br />\nNBA聲明原文如下：<br />\nNBA非常關注香港樂視體育終止賽事轉播的事件。為了實現NBA服務球迷的承諾，NBA將會向成功完成用戶審核的前樂視體育NBA付費會員免費提供NBA League Pass，以觀看包括季後賽及總決賽在內的NBA 2017-18賽季餘下所有賽事。所有賽事及內容均為英文旁述。前樂視體育NBA付費會員可於3月27日中午12時起至4月20日中午12時期間，前往 <a href=\"http://www.nbasignup.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nbasignup.hk&d=qcVMWSBmAn4cc9vk4jlWGXadZns4eLIrfSaUqUvMaEw%3D&h=6003f42e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.nbasignup.hk</a> 申請獲取NBA League Pass用戶代碼。凡是成功通過審核的會員將會免費獲得NBA League Pass用戶代碼，隨後即可於 <a href=\"https://watch.nba.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwatch.nba.com&d=qcVMWSBmAn4cc9vk4jlWGXadZns4eLIrfSaUqUvMaEw%3D&h=7a8bd607\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://watch.nba.com</a> 啟動該代碼觀看賽事。與此同時，我們感謝所有香港球迷多年來對NBA的鼎力支持，未來我們會繼續努力為球迷帶來更多精彩的NBA賽事。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20180326/57996615\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180326%2F57996615&d=qcVMWSBmAn4cc9vk4jlWGXadZns4eLIrfSaUqUvMaEw%3D&h=e69c2a3a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180326%2F57996615&h=7613f2fe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20180326/57996615</a>"},{"pid":"068cd02a56d70e2777d4efe6ba079005883742ed","tid":606037,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T07:43:49.000Z","msg":"識玩公關<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e41839aab9a81c9b216813dcfe07691615b4fce5","tid":606037,"uid":113956,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T11:05:58.000Z","msg":"美帝又要幫支那執手尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"690e4b2f62eca69a428f2065e3b7aad874aa5e9e","tid":606037,"uid":10340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T11:08:34.000Z","msg":"班美國佬近排真係贏左9條街！"}]}